rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:01:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">韡</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">驊</span>已經係唔同字</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cd060b05cc08828f0e884069be578f8952c1b5","tid":1995884,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T20:52:00.000Z","msg":"老鳳一開po，所有食花生的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，「老鳳，你今日又殺咗幾多隻狗？」他不回答，自言自語，「大家睇住啦，分化狗永遠唔撚敢入以下嘅post反駁老鳳，佢地真係支共主力」，便開多個po屈班人做分化狗當駁咗。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又係度推人去死啦！」老鳳睜大眼睛說，「我係提倡緊全民勇武&hellip;&hellip;」「全民勇武？日日見你係啲po度叫人打狗殺狗，但係有行動就唔見你岀手，全民勇武唔包你自己？」老鳳便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「提倡全民勇武，不算是推人去死&hellip;&hellip;只係我無資格帶頭，無話過唔喺後面玩狙&hellip;&hellip;抗爭者的事，能算是推人去死麼」接連便是難懂的話，甚麼「有我係度隻狗死硬」，甚麼「捷克嘅係scorpion非常好用嘅槍」之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來，連登内外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdYfLXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdYfLXw.png&h=2f645353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3xXmHV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3xXmHV.png&h=ce7dfffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BEnXmQw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBEnXmQw.png&h=cced6c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiooneH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiooneH.png&h=a27668c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fcc33b7cc90c5f6756045ff2ac520053c0d0b61","tid":1995884,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T22:03:51.000Z","msg":"湯渣<br />\n大波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ff4c1ccad81b1f893912